sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant MW as MainWindow
    participant ML as MapLoader (bg thread)
    participant GR as GameResources
    participant DFS as DataFileSystem (vfspp/DAT)
    participant RD as MapReader + ProReader
    participant EW as EditorWidget
    participant RE as RenderingEngine (SFML)

    User->>MW: Open map
    MW->>ML: addLoader(path) via LoadingWidget
    activate ML
    ML->>GR: resources
    GR->>DFS: read .map + referenced .pro bytes
    DFS-->>GR: bytes (DAT inflate / native folder)
    ML->>RD: parse .map (proLoadCallback to ProReader)
    RD-->>ML: Map (objects, tiles, scripts)
    deactivate ML
    ML-->>MW: onDone, present errors via hasError()
    MW->>EW: new EditorWidget(resources, map)
    EW->>RE: render frame (TextureManager stitches FRM sheets)
    RE-->>User: rendered map
